metadata.metaValue: float, long, uint, bool, string, Math::float2, Math::float3, Math::float4, Math::float3x3, Math::float4x4, Object

These arrays serve the same purpose of face_offset, but instead of indicating where faces start and end, they tells us where each mesh starts and ends. And similar to face offset, the array length will always be meshes.size + 1
If its not a range geo prop we merge the data arrays and call it a day
